tead, self-fulfillment’s true epistemic significance lies in more local, nuanced philosophical issues such as theory evaluation and the thesis of underdetermination. In presenting a novel framework, this book facilitates deeper engagement with the developing field of self-fulfilling science, and is of interest to philosophers of science, social scientists, and social constructionists.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Aug 2021) 4aHomo Oeconomicus. 4aPerformativität. 4aSelbsterfüllende Prophezeiung. 4aSelbsterfüllende Wissenschaft. 7aPHILOSOPHY / Epistemology.2bisacsh  aSelf-fulfilling science.  ahomo economicus.  aperformativity.  aself-fulfilling prophecy.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Ebook Package English 2021z978311075072008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2021 Part 1z978311075070608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishz978311075400108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Philosophy 2021 Englishz978311075415508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Philosophy 2021z9783110753929oZDB-23-DPH0 cEPUBz97831107465320 cprintz978311074633440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311074640240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110746402423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110746402.jpg  a978-3-11-075070-6  DG Plus DeG Package 2021 Part 1b2021  a978-3-11-075072-0  DG Ebook Package English 2021b2021  a978-3-11-075400-1  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishb2021  a978-3-11-075415-5  EBOOK PACKAGE Philosophy 2021 Englishb2021  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  